UC Velocity ERP - Database Migrations

This directory contains Alembic database migration scripts.

## Quick Reference

Generate a new migration after changing models.py:
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description_of_change"

Apply all pending migrations:
    alembic upgrade head

Rollback one migration:
    alembic downgrade -1

Show current revision:
    alembic current

Show migration history:
    alembic history

## Production

Migrations run automatically on Railway deploy via the releaseCommand
in railway.toml. No manual intervention needed.
